Let's look at our question again: How are you?
让我们再看一下我们的问题：你好吗？

29
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:36,500
This is the most well-known way of asking how someone is.
这是询问别人状况最为人熟知的方式。

30
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,200
