"Not so good"
“不太好”

54
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,100
(slow) Not so good
(慢速) 不太好

55
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:37,800
"Not great"
“不太好”

56
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,500
(slow) Not great.
(慢速) 不太好。

57
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:40,500
